114
00:10:34,581 --> 00:10:36,381
That's right.

115
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:41,820
- Mr. Feng, please accept it.
- Madam Wu.

116
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:46,461
Master Zhang, will you help me?

117
00:10:46,461 --> 00:10:48,420
By your command.

118
00:10:48,420 --> 00:10:50,940
It's a matter of life and death. Do not delay.

119
00:10:50,940 --> 00:10:54,740
Master Zhang, please set out this afternoon.

120
00:10:55,341 --> 00:10:57,020
