185
00:16:30,820 --> 00:16:32,740
When I first saw you,

186
00:16:34,540 --> 00:16:39,740
I swore that I'd protect all of you.

187
00:16:46,141 --> 00:16:48,421
But in the end, I failed.

188
00:16:51,981 --> 00:16:57,181
Guys, impulsiveness serves nothing.

189
00:16:58,180 --> 00:17:00,260
The only thing we can do

190
00:17:01,700 --> 00:17:04,621
is to find our enemy

191
00:17:04,621 --> 00:17:09,861
and avenge Tang Rou and our buddies.

192
00:17:09,861 --> 00:17:14,301
Qiu Shui, the Power Gang is way too powerful.

193
00:17:14,301 --> 00:17:20,341
