194
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:33,220
I know it's difficult.

195
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:39,740
But I'll take them down one day.

196
00:17:42,381 --> 00:17:46,621
Qiu Shui. I believe in you.

197
00:17:46,621 --> 00:17:48,420
Me too.

198
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:51,581
