I want you to have it.

206
00:18:22,460 --> 00:18:24,260
Take care.

207
00:18:32,861 --> 00:18:37,581
Alright, guys. Be very careful.

208
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:42,141
Try to avoid that despicable Kang Chu Yu.

209
00:18:42,141 --> 00:18:45,341
I truly despise that man.

210
00:18:45,341 --> 00:18:47,781
He became a lackey of the Power Gang.

211
00:18:47,781 --> 00:18:51,541
We've been so close to him for years.

212
00:18:51,541 --> 00:18:53,021
My seniors once even said that

213
00:18:53,021 --> 00:18:55,500
he cultivated ice-cold internal energy

214
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:58,541
to unleash the power of the Hanhao Stone,

215
00:18:58,541 --> 00:19:00,621
which was "awe-inspiring".

216
00:19:01,581 --> 00:19:03,381
Unbelievable.

217
00:19:04,101 --> 00:19:09,621
Qiu Shui, we'll get going
and wait to avenge Tang Rou.

218
00:19:10,581 --> 00:19:12,420
Qiu Shui.

219
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:16,220
- Take care.
- Take care.

